\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Who is that?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Ever heard of a demon?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Of course.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Just one.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Well, if I ever see one, I will be sure to\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 \u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Boy, I don\u8217\'92t speak of some nervy, feather-pluckin\u8217\'92 demon. I speak of a beast. }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1\cf1 The}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1  Amalgamete. What I want you to do is open your mouth and spit Mazidfire into its belly. Is that something you\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d be willing to do? Or do you need to bargain.\u8221\'94}
